ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectCUKTCA Tariff Preference Regulations
PrecisCUKTCA TARIFF PREFERENCE REGULATIONS in order to allow eligible goods that are not shipped directly into Canada from the U.K. and certain associated territories to retain the eligibility for preferential tariff rates provided the goods remain under customs control in third countries.
